# Design system

> Full spec in `design.md`. Summary in `AGENTS.md` and `.ai/context/charts-ui.md`.

- CSS tokens only (`--bg`, `--surface`, `--positive`, `--negative`) — no raw hex.
- Green/red reserved for P&L; status uses `--status-*`.
- Mobile-first, both themes, touch targets ≥ 44px.
